## Instructions
##### Create a web page using R Markdown that features a map created with Leaflet.
##### Your webpage must contain the date that you created the document, and it must contain a map created with Leaflet.

## January 25, 2021
```{r echo=TRUE, message=FALSE, warning=FALSE}
library(leaflet)
my_map <- leaflet() %>% addTiles() %>% addMarkers(lat=40.1560, lng=47.1588, popup="Quzanlı, Ağdam, Azərbaycan")
my_map
```
